{"tid":1373546,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開] [文宣上場！！！] 寫左封英文信講黑警今日暴行 麻煩各位Send比各大國際機構/傳媒","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T00:16:34.000Z","uid":97944,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"225a16faa03a5de2540cd174171042ad79fc00ae","tid":1373546,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"(頭先開左去吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n小弟英文不才<br />\n但當見到前綫勇武抗暴個陣<br />\n我Draft左封英文信講黑警今日暴行<br />\n希望國際會將呢樣野connect到去白衣人度<br />\n希望各位巴絲幫下手Copy paste去各大國際傳媒機構<br />\n當然希望有高人可以指點下啲英文<br />\n<br />\nBrutality and Vigilante attacks of Hong Kong Police towards Unarmed Ordinary Citizens<br />\n<br />\nDear Sir/Madam,<br />\n<br />\nI am writing to demand your coverage/attention to the brutality and extreme violence exerted to the ordinary unarmed citizens of Hong Kong by the Hong Kong Police on the 27th July, 2019.<br />\n<br />\nOn the 27th July, there was a peaceful protest in the Yuen Long District in Hong Kong. The protesters opposed against the Triads beating ordinary citizens in the Metro Station on the 21st July, and accused police of their indifference and non-action of this incident despite receiving thousands of emergency calls in 3 hours. <br />\n<br />\nIn this protest, the Police employed brutality towards unarmed peaceful protesters and ordinary citizens. This included firing tear gas to residential buildings, Metro Stations and elderly homes. More importantly, in the evening, hundreds of police entered the MTR station and used brutal force to beat the heads of unarmed peaceful ordinary citizens. Some were injured with blood. Some became unconscious. <br />\n<br />\nThe Police&rsquo;s brutality and vigilante attacks reminded the people of Hong Kong the violence of the Triads on last weekend. The Police had lost their temperament. Not only are they no longer able to protect the lives of Hong Kong citizens, but also become the Triad members themselves to beat us.<br />\n<br />\nI hope you understand that it is difficult to provide sufficient evidence due to the chaotic situation at the scene and the Police prohibiting reporters from filming their actions. Yet, please refer to the attached GIF for your follow-up actions. Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家attach埋以下野做證據：<br />\n1. <img src=\"https://s1.ezgif.com/save/ezgif-1-90f04f850673.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.ezgif.com%2Fsave%2Fezgif-1-90f04f850673.gif&h=3da870dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/350460870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F350460870&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3llQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=386fd1c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/350460870</a> 727 警察射tg去民居<br />\n3. <a href=\"https://foreignaffairs.house.gov/2019/7/engel-statement-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignaffairs.house.gov%2F2019%2F7%2Fengel-statement-on-hong-kong&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3llQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=cf96ef7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://foreignaffairs.house.gov/2019/7/engel-statement-on-hong-kong</a> 美國國會聲明"},{"pid":"e2fe356d338e389400c3390ad9dffba5c68af5a5","tid":1373546,"uid":97944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ArmChannelTV/videos/381362682521959/UzpfSTcwNTU2ODExMzoxMDE1NzQ0OTczNzk4MzExNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FArmChannelTV%2Fvideos%2F381362682521959%2FUzpfSTcwNTU2ODExMzoxMDE1NzQ0OTczNzk4MzExNA%2F&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3llQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=035967e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ArmChannelTV/videos/381362682521959/UzpfSTcwNTU2ODExMzoxMDE1NzQ0OTczNzk4MzExNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n「速龍」突然快速衝入西鐵站突襲<br />\n可以加埋呢條"},{"pid":"e33e89248ac671bf3948a79425eddbde3d6107